 he basic designs and application techniques of&nbsp\; Henna&nbsp\; or&nbsp
 \; Mehendi \, which&nbsp\; is &nbsp\;used to create temporary tattoos. Ple
 ase feel free to bring your friends to learn more about Desi culture and t
 he significance of&nbsp\; Mehendi &nbsp\;in the Indian culture! If you com
 e with a group of more than 7 members\, please email&nbsp\; acc@iu.edu &nb
