DESCRIPTION:Hosted by: Health Promotion\n\nJoin us for Mindful Makers\, a 
 weekly event built around being creative\, meeting new people and feeling 
 more confident in yourself and your wellness. Each week has a theme - come
  for one or come for all! We're here to have fun and make cool things. Jan
 uary 21: Semester Vision Boards Picture your new semester! Create a vision
  board that will motivate you to achieve this semester. Learn some tips on
  how to set great goals to help you achieve that vision. &nbsp\; January 2
 8: Meditation and Aromatherapy Ever been curious about aromatherapy and ho
 w it works? Here's your opportunity to learn more! While you're here\, we'
 ll also practice deep breathing techniques\, progressive relaxation and gu
 ided visualization\, and other simple techniques that don't require any sp
 ecial skills or equipment &nbsp\; February 4: Crochet the Stress Away Whet
 her you're a crochet expert or have never picked up a hook in your life\, 
 we have a place for you! Join us\, learn basic crochet stitch
LOCATION:Wellness House
URL:https://iub.campuslabs.com/engage/event/11977507
X-SOURCE:IU beINvolved Student Orgs
END:VEVENT
