BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:A Kid Again General Meeting
DTSTART;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260420T230000Z
DTEND;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260421T000000Z
UID:https://iub.campuslabs.com/engage/event/11951975
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://se-images.campuslabs.com/clink/images/4c
 6af4d6-cc7c-40ac-9832-a8ad92a2be3e72b28d2e-35ae-4e77-bb50-95ea60f38f7f.png
DESCRIPTION:Hosted by: A Kid Again IU\n\nJoin A Kid Again for our biweekly
  meeting! A Kid Again IU is one of three Collegiate Chapters that have bee
 n serving families for over 25 years. A Kid Again gives families who have 
 a child struggling with a life-threatening diagnosis a chance to make uniq
 ue memories through our free\, monthly Adventures and fun events organized
  by A Kid Again. As a collegiate chapter\, our support comes in three ways
 : volunteering\, philanthropy\, and outreach.&nbsp\; We would absolutely l
 ove to have you join our organization and help us achieve our goals as a C
 ollegiate Chapter and a National Chapter!
LOCATION:IMU Maple Room
URL:https://iub.campuslabs.com/engage/event/11951975
X-SOURCE:IU beINvolved Student Orgs
END:VEVENT
