 s&ndash\;based duo of Mica Tenenbaum and Matthew Lewin is known for infect
 ious hooks\, synth-heavy beats\, and a wildly immersive pop sound that&rsq
 uo\;s made them a must-see live act. Make plans to join in for a night of 
